name: Skull Octopus
description: An Octopus invading a golden human skull. The skull then becomes part of it's identity.  What was once a wise creature has now evolved into a fearsome monster. In life we wear many masks, and in the process we loose our old selves, our true selves. But we do this because the world is a scary place.  Change is necessary for survival. And there will be times in life when we will need to leave our comfort zones and play the monster's part.
